<http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/blogspot/hsDu/~3/bwWDZrOb82c/new-course-on-developing-android-apps.html|New Course on Developing Android Apps for Google Cast and Android TV>
Posted by <https://google.com/+JBGordon/|Josh Gordon>, Developer Advocate

Go where your users are: the living room! Google Cast lets users stream their favorite apps from Android, iOS and the Web right onto their TV. Android TV turns a TV into an Android device, only bigger!
